<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="extra-adv">extra <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ekstrə/    美 /'ekstrə/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>额外地；特别地；非常：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>work extra hard
工作特别努力</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>paid extra</strong> for a good room.
为了住个好房间，我额外付费了。</p></div></div>